Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.07,0:00:46.11,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{OP}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.41,0:02:16.45,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Part A}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.63,0:10:05.67,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Part B}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.48,0:22:53.52,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{ED}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.47,0:24:08.51,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Epilogue}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.48,0:24:16.52,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Preview}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.37,0:00:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to the Velvet Room.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.27,0:00:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The Persona ability is the power to control one's heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.92,0:00:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,and the heart is strengthened through bonds.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.19,0:00:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,By becoming involved with others and forming bonds,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.75,0:00:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,you were able to obtain the Magician Arcana.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.41,0:00:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Your power will grow as your bond deepens.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.11,0:00:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I strongly urge you to take this to heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.97,0:00:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, I bid you farewell, until we meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.23,0:02:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.30,0:02:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,He's cute! Is he yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.68,0:02:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I found him,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.77,0:02:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,but my parents said to get rid of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.52,0:02:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,He's going to be all alone again!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.52,0:02:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.65,0:02:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Satonaka Chie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.14,0:03:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Amagi Yukiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.25,0:03:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meetcha, Yukiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.04,0:03:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And you too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.64,0:03:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.15,0:03:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.60,0:03:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.71,0:03:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.57,0:03:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Satonaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.24,0:03:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Yukiko here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.40,0:03:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Amagi? Nope, I haven't seen her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.45,0:03:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap! What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.52,0:03:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.81,0:03:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Last night, on the Midnight Channel...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.59,0:03:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we were just talking about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.13,0:03:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I saw Yukiko on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.67,0:03:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I've seen her in that kimono before.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.88,0:04:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\t(2860,3402,\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&)}She wore it during that one interview.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.97,0:04:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been texting her, but she hasn't responded.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.60,0:04:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Tried calling?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.77,0:04:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It just goes straight to voicemail.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.35,0:04:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't think Amagi—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.77,0:04:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't even go there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.90,0:04:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.86,0:04:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,She's okay. She's probably just busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.45,0:04:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Or she could've lost her cell.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.30,0:04:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,She might be busy helping at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.04,0:04:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! That's gotta be it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.58,0:04:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna drop by the inn!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.58,0:04:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You're leaving? But the bell's about to ring!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.46,0:04:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.62,0:04:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.26,0:04:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank God!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.97,0:04:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You're there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.38,0:04:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah! Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.80,0:04:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.64,0:04:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll text you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.56,0:04:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What a relief!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.06,0:04:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,She's been busy 'cause a group came in without reservations.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.63,0:04:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But if it wasn't Amagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.61,0:04:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Who was on the Midnight Channel?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.95,0:05:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.91,0:05:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, that handwriting sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.33,0:05:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I took notes for Yukiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.79,0:05:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Gotcha...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.91,0:05:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Careful on the way down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.63,0:05:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! You the transfer student?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.68,0:05:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,T-That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.30,0:05:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you played much basketball?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.56,0:05:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.97,0:05:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.31,0:05:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.15,0:05:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Tough luck, Ichijo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.40,0:05:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be waiting if you change your mind, new guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.11,0:05:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Even inexperienced sophomores are welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.58,0:05:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really crowded today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.33,0:05:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, try sticking your hand in and calling him over.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.71,0:06:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.72,0:06:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Something bit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.23,0:06:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It left bite marks! Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.93,0:06:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's making me cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.76,0:06:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.89,0:06:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that Chie I hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.27,0:06:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up? Is this a new game?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.52,0:06:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Teddie, does it feel like anyone's in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.60,0:06:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's "anyone"? I'm a lonely little bear like always.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.07,0:06:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,This land feels so bear-ren.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.99,0:06:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.65,0:06:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're sure no one's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.86,0:06:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm not lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.95,0:06:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,My nose is running as good as ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.03,0:06:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone showed up on the Midnight Channel yesterday, even though no one's there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.37,0:06:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.15,0:06:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's check it out again tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.65,0:06:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.15,0:07:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Tonight, I'm gonna score myself a hot stud!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.91,0:07:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to "Not a Dream, Not a Hoax"!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.62,0:07:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,"Princess Yukiko's Hunt for Her Prince Charming"!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.46,0:07:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And I came prepared!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.38,0:07:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,My lacy unmentionables are ready to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.01,0:07:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like my heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.26,0:07:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm out to catch a whole harem of only the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.39,0:07:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.97,0:07:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, did you see that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.03,0:07:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I'd taped it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.39,0:08:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.58,0:08:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.31,0:08:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's your dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.06,0:08:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,He left already.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.64,0:08:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,He said he's gonna be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.85,0:08:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.00,0:08:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah, with my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.90,0:08:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be fine by myself. I can hold the fort.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.90,0:08:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}High pressure is moving in,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.62,0:08:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}so we should have clear skies all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.08,0:08:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Let's see what to expect for the—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.94,0:08:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gonna be sunny. I should do some laundry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.44,0:08:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,See you tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.29,0:08:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,See you later then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.13,0:08:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Narukami!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.06,0:08:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.68,0:09:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What kept you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.69,0:09:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I found some stuff we can use in my closet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.98,0:09:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatcha think?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.69,0:09:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanamura, are those...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.69,0:09:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, the blades are fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.40,0:09:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Which one strikes your fancy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.86,0:09:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.24,0:09:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe both would be good too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.70,0:09:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Two suspicious young males found,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.96,0:09:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,one armed with multiple weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.33,0:09:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hold it! No, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.59,0:09:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Are you resisting arrest?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.84,0:09:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We weren't doing anything! We aren't the bad guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.42,0:09:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We're just huge sword fanatics!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.88,0:09:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.05,0:09:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,They're over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.14,0:09:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.45,0:09:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.82,0:09:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.20,0:09:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanamura! Narukami!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.74,0:09:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.41,0:09:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukiko's..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.30,0:10:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, guys. Don't stir up trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.01,0:10:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,If you weren't Dojima's nephew and his friend, you wouldn't have gotten off so lightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.77,0:10:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.16,0:10:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanamura!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.34,0:10:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.33,0:10:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Satonaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.40,0:10:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Yukiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.52,0:10:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Amagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.25,0:10:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,She's gone missing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.24,0:10:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,She was definitely home last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.49,0:10:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But no one's seen her since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.58,0:10:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, Amagi Yukiko's family asked us to help search for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.16,0:10:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you her friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.96,0:10:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.96,0:10:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Did anything stick out as unusual?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.09,0:10:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Did Yukiko seem troubled?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.95,0:10:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Troubled?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.01,0:10:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Ms. Yamano was staying at the Amagi Inn before the first murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.80,0:11:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems she had some harsh words for the manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.89,0:11:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And Yukiko's...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.90,0:11:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,She's the manager's daughter,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.52,0:11:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,so there's been some theories that she's laying low for some reason or another.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.57,0:11:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.45,0:11:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You think Yukiko's the murderer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.91,0:11:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No, it's just a rumor floating—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.57,0:11:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Like hell it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.66,0:11:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Satonaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.16,0:11:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.74,0:11:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm not saying—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.50,0:11:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You implied Yukiko—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.50,0:11:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's going on here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.31,0:11:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.04,0:11:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Satonaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.75,0:11:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukiko...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.26,0:11:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukiko is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.38,0:11:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.26,0:11:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Nothing, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.43,0:11:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We've gotta save Yukiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.19,0:11:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.82,0:11:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't this on the Midnight Channel last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.78,0:12:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Satonaka, you should wait out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.78,0:12:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going! I'm definitely going!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.83,0:12:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Once she's made up her mind, you can't stop her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.41,0:12:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Teddie, is Amagi in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.79,0:12:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No doubt about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.58,0:12:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,My nose is onto the scent!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.67,0:12:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't run off on your own!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.22,0:12:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.33,0:12:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't leave me behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.26,0:12:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukiko! Yukiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.86,0:12:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,She's really oblivious of her surroundings.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.86,0:12:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanamura!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.74,0:12:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.24,0:12:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Persona!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.96,0:12:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's rumble, Persona!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.39,0:13:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Way to go, Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.89,0:13:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiraiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.16,0:13:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yosuke, you've got a lot to learn.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.37,0:13:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't I get any respect?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.66,0:13:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.58,0:13:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukiko... Yukiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.42,0:13:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.30,0:13:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this Yukiko's room?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.68,0:13:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,She said red looks good on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.60,0:13:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.30,0:13:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate the name Yukiko, meaning "snow child."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.37,0:13:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Snow is cold, and it melts quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.73,0:13:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's transient, worthless.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.74,0:14:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's perfect for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.65,0:14:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Yukiko, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.23,0:14:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.23,0:14:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Aside from inheriting the inn, I'm absolutely worthless.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.56,0:14:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Answer me, Yukiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.53,0:14:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Yukiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.24,0:14:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, Chie told me that red looks good on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.86,0:14:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Chie was the only one who gave my life meaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.63,0:14:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Chie is bright and strong, and she can do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.97,0:14:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,She has everything that I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.97,0:14:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Compared to Chie, I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.69,0:14:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Chie protects me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.98,0:14:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,She looks after my worthless life. Chie is so kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.32,0:14:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukiko, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.99,0:14:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,"Chie is so kind," huh? What a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.63,0:14:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.32,0:14:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.71,0:14:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.00,0:14:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Satonaka Chie.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.96,0:15:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying? {\i1}I'm{\i0} Satonaka Chie.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.50,0:15:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I'm also Satonaka Chie.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.63,0:15:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on? This is crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.60,0:15:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukiko said that I'm protecting her?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.44,0:15:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,She said she's worthless!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.33,0:15:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You gotta love that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.77,0:15:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.19,0:15:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukiko's so good-looking, so feminine, so fair-skinned.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.32,0:15:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,She's the one all the guys drool over.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.24,0:15:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,When Yukiko looked at me with such jealousy...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.49,0:15:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, did I get a charge out of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.41,0:15:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, Yukiko can't do anything without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.55,0:15:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.81,0:15:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.73,0:15:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one standing on top!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.93,0:15:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,No! That's now how I feel at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.56,0:15:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You okay, Satonaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.31,0:15:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.59,0:15:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,No, don't come near me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.35,0:15:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.02,0:16:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No, this isn't me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.57,0:16:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Satonaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.90,0:16:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.33,0:16:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit! There are so many!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.37,0:16:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you're wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.58,0:16:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you're just gonna turn your back and deny me again?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.71,0:16:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.92,0:16:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not... You're not...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.34,0:16:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Satonaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.86,0:16:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.27,0:16:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I am a Shadow... The true self...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.53,0:16:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.53,0:16:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Satonaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.16,0:16:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get in my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.25,0:17:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I see that you're gonna protect the "real" me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.34,0:17:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you're gonna pay the price!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.84,0:17:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Master, you're the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.98,0:17:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanamura!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.07,0:17:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.78,0:17:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Just die already!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.95,0:17:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be sure to take good care of Yukiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.03,0:17:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,As my footstool, that is!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.58,0:17:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,A stool?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.85,0:17:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I'm the one who can't do anything on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.33,0:17:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.75,0:17:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But Yukiko depends on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.96,0:17:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why she's my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.59,0:17:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't lose her!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.32,0:17:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.35,0:17:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Satonaka, don't let her trick you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.72,0:17:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Silence!{17:59}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.77,0:18:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanamura!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.63,0:18:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not trying to trick her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.69,0:18:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,These are my true colors.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.11,0:18:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,My true colors, I say!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.87,0:18:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukiko's so pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.68,0:18:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,She's the one all the boys drool over.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.99,0:18:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,They're me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.87,0:18:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, they represent how you really feel,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.25,0:18:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,jealous and envious.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.49,0:18:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Without me around, she can't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.76,0:18:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,She'd be nothing without me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.68,0:18:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,No... No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.93,0:18:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.84,0:18:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,These are my true colors?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.77,0:18:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,How horrible...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.78,0:18:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Who cares if they are?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.56,0:18:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still her friend, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.21,0:19:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.67,0:19:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,They're right, Yukiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.54,0:19:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We're friends, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.88,0:19:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the inner "me" that I pretended never existed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.22,0:19:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the part of me I couldn't face.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.04,0:19:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're still me, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.86,0:19:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Satonaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.90,0:19:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut the crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.53,0:19:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you seriously gonna acknowledge my existence and accept me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.97,0:19:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Narukami!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.59,0:19:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.04,0:19:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna tear you to pieces!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.88,0:19:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanamura!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.26,0:19:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, dear! Yosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.43,0:19:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanamura!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.55,0:20:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\t(4777,5069,\3c&HFFFFFF&,\4c&HFFFFFF&)}You have established a new bond, allowing you to use another Arcana.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.93,0:20:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You possess the power to wield multiple Personas.{sic, but that's how the game does it}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.19,0:20:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It is the wild card,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.52,0:20:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,O Chosen One.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.80,0:20:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Chosen One?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.24,0:20:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Change!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.91,0:20:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Pyro Jack!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.42,0:20:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my! Oh, my!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.84,0:20:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No fair! He gets to use two Personas?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.97,0:20:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Get her!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.06,0:20:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanamura!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.98,0:20:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.25,0:21:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You're me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.86,0:21:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.68,0:21:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,A Persona.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.15,0:21:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is my...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.20,0:21:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.49,0:21:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my Persona...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.67,0:22:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right. Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.46,0:22:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,He looks busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.37,0:22:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so lame.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.51,0:22:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukiko could die the next time it gets foggy over here,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.98,0:22:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,but I can't do anything about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.19,0:22:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't accept that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.19,0:22:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You aren't lame.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.23,0:22:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure we'll need your help to save Amagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.78,0:22:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.28,0:22:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,As a token of my gratitude, I'll show you something special.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.95,0:22:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.33,0:22:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.33,0:22:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a fatass and stinks like no other,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.21,0:22:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,but he's the one who broke the ice and introduced me to Yukiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.06,0:22:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.44,0:24:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Chie!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.60,0:24:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get in my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.90,0:24:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, partner!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.07,0:24:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.07,0:24:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that from back then?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.19,0:24:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.11,0:24:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sick of these damn chains!
